00:43:15.531 --> 00:43:16.030 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:43:16.030 --> 00:43:17.596 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: Did I say that?

00:43:17.596 --> 00:43:19.100 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah, you said that.

00:43:19.100 --> 00:43:19.460 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: Yeah, yeah.

00:43:19.460 --> 00:43:21.460 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So let's talk
about where it's buried

00:43:21.460 --> 00:43:23.120 align:middle line:84%
