in plain sight.

00:43:23.120 --> 00:43:25.690 align:middle line:84%
You talked about
the one in Chartres,

00:43:25.690 --> 00:43:28.120 align:middle line:84%
the information that was
embedded there in these four

00:43:28.120 --> 00:43:30.860 align:middle line:90%
distinct 5,600-year cycles.

00:43:30.860 --> 00:43:33.500 align:middle line:84%
>>CARLSON: Yes, and
that same depiction

00:43:33.500 --> 00:43:36.880 align:middle line:84%
