1200 1300 AD, but for 2100 AD.

00:44:07.140 --> 00:44:11.980 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Absolutely, to help
us regain, A, some memory,

00:44:11.980 --> 00:44:13.600 align:middle line:90%
and give us a heads up.

00:44:13.600 --> 00:44:14.630 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: Yes.

00:44:14.630 --> 00:44:18.670 align:middle line:84%
Now, salient example--
Sphinx in Egypt,

00:44:18.670 --> 00:44:22.249 align:middle line:84%
