into a time where--

00:52:52.630 --> 00:52:56.330 align:middle line:84%
and I referred to this earlier--
there's this mass amnesia.

00:52:56.330 --> 00:52:58.940 align:middle line:84%
We're desperately seeking
clues as to our past.

00:52:58.940 --> 00:53:01.750 align:middle line:84%
And people like you and others
are finding these clues now

00:53:01.750 --> 00:53:04.530 align:middle line:84%
that have been laid down
there for us to see,

00:53:04.530 --> 00:53:06.057 align:middle line:84%
hiding in plain
sight for all of us.

00:53:06.057 --> 00:53:07.390 align:middle line:90%
>>CARLSON: Hiding in plain site.

00:53:07.390 --> 00:53:10.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: We have
this systemic fear

00:53:10.520 --> 00:53:13.139 align:middle line:84%
