00:54:03.880 --> 00:54:04.520 align:middle line:90%
Why now?

00:54:04.520 --> 00:54:05.570 align:middle line:90%
We're remembering now.

00:54:05.570 --> 00:54:09.150 align:middle line:84%
>>CARLSON: If we look at
the hard scientific record,

00:54:09.150 --> 00:54:12.010 align:middle line:84%
