of the planet has oscillated.

00:54:16.016 --> 00:54:17.390 align:middle line:84%
And there have
been periods where

00:54:17.390 --> 00:54:20.030 align:middle line:84%
the glaciers have grown
enormously and then

00:54:20.030 --> 00:54:21.480 align:middle line:90%
rapidly shrunk away.

00:54:21.480 --> 00:54:24.360 align:middle line:84%
